WEBVTT
X-TIMESTAMP-MAP=MPEGTS:181083,LOCAL:00:00:00.000

00:23:00.176 --> 00:23:01.466 A:middle
&gt;&gt; Thanks, John.

00:23:01.856 --> 00:23:03.736 A:middle
INSIDE is an eerie adventure

00:23:03.736 --> 00:23:05.556 A:middle
filled with intrigue and danger.

00:23:05.676 --> 00:23:08.396 A:middle
You play as an unnamed boy as he

00:23:08.396 --> 00:23:09.746 A:middle
struggled through a dystopian

00:23:09.746 --> 00:23:10.076 A:middle
world.

00:23:10.516 --> 00:23:12.876 A:middle
By solving puzzles, you uncover

00:23:12.876 --> 00:23:14.156 A:middle
an alarming environment of

00:23:14.156 --> 00:23:15.476 A:middle
lifeless bodies and their

00:23:15.476 --> 00:23:16.536 A:middle
violent controllers.

00:23:17.026 --> 00:23:18.626 A:middle
But buried under this dark

00:23:18.626 --> 00:23:20.126 A:middle
premise is a brilliantly

00:23:20.126 --> 00:23:21.406 A:middle
designed game.

00:23:21.906 --> 00:23:23.566 A:middle
A worthy successor to Playdead's

00:23:23.566 --> 00:23:25.576 A:middle
first game, Limbo, INSIDE also

00:23:25.576 --> 00:23:27.136 A:middle
uses a monochromatic palette,

00:23:27.506 --> 00:23:28.906 A:middle
which places your focus solely

00:23:28.906 --> 00:23:30.016 A:middle
on the details of the

00:23:30.016 --> 00:23:31.686 A:middle
environment and the animation.

00:23:32.136 --> 00:23:33.026 A:middle
Check it out as he actually

00:23:33.026 --> 00:23:34.346 A:middle
pulls and struggles to get these

00:23:34.436 --> 00:23:35.466 A:middle
boards off the wall.

00:23:35.956 --> 00:23:37.086 A:middle
So, cool.

00:23:38.206 --> 00:23:39.626 A:middle
INSIDE's chilling soundtrack

00:23:39.686 --> 00:23:41.046 A:middle
reinforces its sinister

00:23:41.046 --> 00:23:41.656 A:middle
atmosphere.

00:23:42.466 --> 00:23:43.606 A:middle
Playdead's audio designers,

00:23:43.606 --> 00:23:44.736 A:middle
actually, used a contact

00:23:44.736 --> 00:23:46.546 A:middle
microphone on a human skull to

00:23:46.546 --> 00:23:47.946 A:middle
create many of the sound effects

00:23:47.946 --> 00:23:48.966 A:middle
that you hear in the game.

00:23:48.966 --> 00:23:50.906 A:middle
Let's listen in.

00:23:51.016 --> 00:23:53.016 A:middle
[ Scraping Sound ]

00:23:53.016 --> 00:23:55.016 A:middle
[ Bang Sound ]

00:23:55.516 --> 00:24:01.516 A:middle
[ Running Footsteps ]

